{"type": "article", "id": 2747, "title": "Chanel x Monster 联名耳机", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-10T08:04:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232515T0PqAIF9OL1pnbZG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tChanel 日前联手耳机制造商 Monster 推出一款联名头戴式耳机，将于本月正式发售。作为时尚与科技界的跨界联名作品，这款耳机在设计上主要以 Chanel 的经典黑色为主调，搭配以菱形元素细节和听筒部分的双 C 标志呈现，每款耳机还将设有一个特别打造的 Chanel 耳机包，为用户带来最为奢华的视觉和听觉享受。据悉，这款耳机的售价将达到 5000 美元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232513C31h2svqQL6OguTI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232513CO3Gyh5P2L6s7lfq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232514TFVbO9RItUE35niM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232514xaDGkEoO9d2QHFIe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232515iJfGLBYNAc68wrQo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}